import React from 'react'
import './loginPage.css'

const LoginPage = () => {
    return(
        <>


            <form>
            <label for="login">Username or Email</label>
            <input type="text" className="login-input" id="login" placeholder="Enter your enail or username here"></input>
            <label for="pass">Password</label>
            <input type="text" className="login-input" id="pass" placeholder="Enter your password here"></input>

            <button type="submit" className="login-btns" id="login-pg-libtn">Login</button>
            <button type="submit" className="login-btns" id="login-pg-clbtn">Cancel</button>
            </form>
           
        </>
    );
}

export default LoginPage
